      <title>无论发生什么，企业的战争风险都将意味着更高的价格</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/15/business/economy/iran-war-inflation-supply-chains.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一个更加危险和不可预测的世界中开展业务将花费更多成本，从而推高从食品到电子产品的所有商品的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/15/business/economy/iran-war-inflation-supply-chains.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 16:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
