    <item>
      <title>特朗普向 ICE 施压，要求其恢复因致命枪击事件而暂停的交通站点</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/15/us/politics/trump-ice-traffic-stops.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[移民和海关执法局在过去一周枪杀两人后，于周二命令其官员停止全国大部分车辆停靠站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/15/us/politics/trump-ice-traffic-stops.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 15:39:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>父亲称，在缅因州被 ICE 杀害的哥伦比亚移民拥有合法身份</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/joan-sebastian-guerrero-maine-ice-shooting.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一被联邦移民特工枪杀的琼·塞巴斯蒂安·格雷罗 (Joan Sebastian Guerrero) 的父亲表示，他的儿子一直在打两份工来养活妻子和女儿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/joan-sebastian-guerrero-maine-ice-shooting.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 15:37:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于以色列来说，美国与伊朗的敌对行动造成了不安的困境</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/15/world/middleeast/israel-us-iran-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们认为，与无法遏制伊朗对以色列构成威胁的协议相比，恢复全面战争更为可取。与此同时，他们等待。]]></description>
