    <item>
      <title>如何远离环孢子虫（一种导致严重肠道疾病的寄生虫）</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/well/eat/cyclospora-stomach-bug-prevention.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[环孢子虫是一种导致肠道疾病的寄生虫，它正在让美国各地的许多人患病。健康专家提供了避免感染的建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/well/eat/cyclospora-stomach-bug-prevention.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 14:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
