    <item>
      <title>环孢子虫已经很难调查。资金削减让事情变得更加困难。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/15/well/eat/cyclospora-outbreak-response.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这种寄生虫已导致美国各地数千人患病，而且众所周知，这种寄生虫很难追踪。资金削减并没有让这项工作变得更容易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/15/well/eat/cyclospora-outbreak-response.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 09:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
